    comment: '<p><strong>Image</strong> elements display pictures that are stored online. Image elements are unique because they are <em>self-enclosing elements</em>, which means that do not have a separate closing tag and are written as a single tag like this:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-html">&#x3C;img src="logo.png" />\n</code></pre>\n<p>The image tag will appear in a webpage like this:  </p>\n<p><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" width="320" height="115"><defs><linearGradient id="b" x1="50%" x2="50%" y1="0%" y2="100%"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#404956"/><stop offset="100%" stop-opacity=".5"/></linearGradient><path id="a" d="M20 20h205v75H20z"/></defs><g fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><rect width="320" height="115" fill="#FFF" rx="9"/><use fill="#292C33" xlink:href="#a"/><use fill="url(#b)" xlink:href="#a"/><path fill="#FFF" fill-opacity=".6" d="M56.46429 53.91184v4.0197l-10.125 6.31669 10.125 6.31668v4.0197L42 65.39672v-2.29697l14.46429-9.1879zM183.75 42.42697h3.47143l-12.15 37.32584H171.6l12.15-37.32584zm5.78571 11.48487L204 63.09974v2.29698l-14.46429 9.1879V70.5649l10.125-6.31668-10.125-6.31668v-4.0197z"/><path fill="#FFF" fill-opacity=".6" d="M56.46429 53.91184v4.0197l-10.125 6.31669 10.125 6.31668v4.0197L42 65.39672v-2.29697l14.46429-9.1879zM183.75 42.42697h3.47143l-12.15 37.32584H171.6l12.15-37.32584zm5.78571 11.48487L204 63.09974v2.29698l-14.46429 9.1879V70.5649l10.125-6.31668-10.125-6.31668v-4.0197z"/><path fill="#F96E44" d="M64.68 63.11672v-.25924c0-11.3852 4.91021-17.07772 14.73078-17.07772 2.05597 0 3.92054.31866 5.59376.95597 1.67321.6373 3.00192 1.38803 3.98616 2.25218.98425.86415 1.84818 1.99293 2.59183 3.38638.74365 1.39344 1.27404 2.57623 1.59119 3.5484.31715.97217.5632 2.14956.73818 3.5322.17498 1.33944.26246 2.18198.26246 2.52764v1.42584l-.13123 2.3332H69.6012c.3062 3.32698 1.33418 5.74117 3.08394 7.24263 1.74977 1.50147 4.34157 2.25219 7.7755 2.25219 4.42448 0 7.99401-.67553 10.68634-2.04